{
  "stem": "5891.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We get into that one wagon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There's so many people there put in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And no pee pee, there is no nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had some straw in the corner.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You had to do your thing there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Anyway, we didn't get out of there for three days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were in there for three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Night and day and occasionally in big cities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I guess we had to stop, till another train, we were connected again and connected again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Until on the end, that whole train was just full of prisoners, [GERMAN], what we call them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish people, Gypsy people, Polish people, political people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All kinds in the different wagons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as far as the toiletry was concerned, I forget to tell, you there was straw in the thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And here is 14-year-old girls, 15-year-old girls, young women, and wives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the men were so nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Made little circles with their backs, turned the backs, and we could do our little business there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The men themselves were very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All strange people, you don't never met.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they got to talking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there had a rumor here, and there was a rumor there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And everybody heard something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it all melted down to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, three days later, we did stop in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Creak!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "With those boxcars or whatever you call them now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my mom was petrified.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, when you're young, you're not quite that petrified.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't expect all this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Even if you told it to me then, it wouldn't have affected me like that, until you actually get into the situation.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "14.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was more concerned about the little ones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That [GERMAN], and taking like mothers that stay together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We don't want to get lost, we don't want to get lost.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
